{"tid":1844774,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻狗有狗瘟 可以點做","createTime":"2020-01-26T19:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T11:21:16.000Z","uid":20962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11d1b10a192fd420799b57635dcae0f2cb8b9ba8","tid":1844774,"uid":20962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"松鼠狗3個月大 打左一針 <br />\n一開始見佢流鼻水冇咩精神 就帶佢去帶獸醫 點知一check發現係狗瘟 <br />\n睇左幾個醫生都話冇得醫 要靠佢自己食野 增強抵抗力 另外比左啲抗生素喂佢食<br />\n咁狗狗一路都好肯食野 係精神差左啲 但都好肯跑 係有咳同流鼻水咁<br />\n點知過左7日 即係前幾日 佢突然開始抽搐 精神好差 唔願玩 唔知呢啲係咪就係啲病毒入侵左神經搞到咁<br />\n有冇人知可以點做 佢keep左都肯食野 一日食4-5餐 但都係惡化左 我仲可以點樣幫佢 有冇人有經驗可以教下我 我唔想放棄佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17b982b7d86ba4005d989a9b25a412f60d87d5b","tid":1844774,"uid":325368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T19:26:14.000Z","msg":"讚佢 叫佢食多啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1039585f15967ce73990c7ba10981e553f75fe91","tid":1844774,"uid":27807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"唔識，希望你隻狗仔會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f3354306b4cc153b5c244c830da14d98c59e33","tid":1844774,"uid":279927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:02:13.000Z","msg":"你要跟我方法做<br />\n1，去買貴西沙比佢食<br />\n2，唔好比佢四處跑，要放<br />\n3，比毛巾圍住佢，要厚毛巾<br />\n4，要清潔的人飲的水，<br />\n5，比佢自己 休息多D，唔好同佢玩<br />\n6，每幾個鐘留意下佢，<br />\n7，只有等"},{"pid":"0634c399ccf90d8d892f275f6a24f5a9e45fd8e1","tid":1844774,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"買番黎？9成都病狗 冇乜可以做 個醫生都係安慰下你 有幾多狗瘟可以靠自己好番"},{"pid":"102d224e0b0987ed0698b423e38bf54d3d8e75c6","tid":1844774,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"拍多啲影片，比多啲好野佢食、陪佢行最後呢一關"},{"pid":"a78c3c0b4dd69e3f605d393cc551b4cfffb51905","tid":1844774,"uid":215026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"邊度買隻病狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfb1513c60b7652644c661c46e65e37b27be88c","tid":1844774,"uid":156992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"請問樓主隻狗狗點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}